<h3>รายละเอียด</h3>
KMUTT cyclist circle is an online platform for all KMUTT cycling teams to exchange information about their biking activities.

Our KMUTT cyclist circle includes the Bike Friday community, the Saturday Ride Fever group, the Pro-Cycling Team, the Green Bike Club, 
the RoboRiders, the Ride to meet U group, etc. And the circle is quickly expanding. 
Our circle has a broad variety of activities ranging from beginning to pro cycling. There is a group for any one to join and the door is always open.

KMUTT would like to encourage our members; students, faculties, and staff, to bike to school or work which resulting in a lifestyle that is not only healthy, 
but also friendly to the environment. It is our goal to set up an example for people to follow. Together we could create a community with less gasoline 
consumption and more energy sustainability. It would direct our country to the greener and better future. KMUTT Green University. 

